reviewText: Remembered this movie from when I was in junior high school.  Couldn't resist seeing if it was still as funny as my memoriy was of it.  It passed!  Some are not as funny as I remembered but overall it still regularly brings a guilty laugh.  We were weird back then to say the least.
summary: From the past - SIlly but still strangly funny

reviewText: I was hoping this was like Amazon Women on the Moon or Kentucky Fried Movie. Instead, it was filmed like a low budget porno and the acting and story was non-existent. Do not waste your time on this one.
